commits.message: Fruit crates can only be stored in large boxes and now have a weight to them
Added a way to get diamond back from password doors
Passwords expire after a weeek of inactivity
Feathers on bowler hat

Snowball fix
Cage of birds match other cage items
Silver on flat stone shouldn't spawn naturally
Hot copper bloom can be picked back up

Copper ore stack with tongs
added missing silver transitions
added missing silver transitions

rearranged jungle tree spawning
All trees are now blocking
Decay for dry fruit tree saplings

Animation for caged birds and removed permanent tag
Can no longer increase hive if honey is present
Vinyards are no longer blocking
Removed odd transition for firing kiln
Fixed cut ball of thread bug
Trellis can be removed
Caged birds and caging rabbits doesn't consume snare
Added branch variants and transitions

Added new cut tree variations
Added CCM Trees - Thanks Mofo and the CCM team!
